Create The Top Left Line And Stacked Column Chart 12

1. Copy and Paste the formatted Fleers Killed | Date chart below.

2. Move the duplicate copy to the left top side of the dashboard

 3. Change the Shared Axis  Values to Race 

4. Change the title to Fleers Killed | Race

5. On the filter pane, click on the dropdown on race. Click on select all, then, deselect "Blank" and "Other"

6. On the visualization pane, click on format. Then adjust the following;
